name: Grab Your Mug Cozy - In Eclectic - READY TO SHIP
description:
What a eco-friendly trendy way to drink your coffee, tea or favorite beverage. My cup cozies are designed to keep your fingers safe from the hot liquid of your coffee cup or the cold condensation of your cold drinks. Each cozy easily fits a standard size coffee mug. These cozies are environmentally safe and friendly. Soft and flexible they fold up quickly and easily to keep in your bag, pocket or car. They are also easy to care for, hand wash and lay flat to dry.

So, next time you grab you mug wrap it in style!
